title: Search for identity of woman found on Melbourne beach | Daily Mail Online
text: Do you know this young woman? Mystery surrounds body in a swimsuit found on a Melbourne beach - as police release images of her face and clothing Victoria police made a public appeal to help identify a lifeless woman's body They have issued computer generated image and pictures of her clothing The body was discovered about 6.50am on Tuesday morning on the Bay Trail Footage from scene shows the body on sand has been covered by a white sheet The woman is yet to be identified, her death is not being treated as suspicious Published: 05:36 GMT, 1 February 2017 | Updated: 05:40 GMT, 1 February 2017 117 shares
